        "rich_text_KFEFt3": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Heading",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h1>How to Match Jewelry with Outfits: The Ultimate Style Guide</h1>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_8DL9Df": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1st Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Jewelry is more than just an accessory—it is a statement of style and personality. Knowing how to match jewelry with outfits can elevate your look, whether you’re dressing for a casual day out, a formal event, or a traditional celebration. In this guide, we’ll walk you through tips and strategies to coordinate your jewelry perfectly with different outfits, helping you create a polished and stylish appearance.</p><h3>Understanding Jewelry and Outfit Compatibility</h3><p>Before you start pairing jewelry with your wardrobe, it’s important to understand the basics. Jewelry comes in various forms necklaces, <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/all-earrings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Earrings\">earrings</a>, bracelets, rings, and more. Each type has its unique way of complementing your outfit. Similarly, outfits can be categorized into casual wear, formal wear, and traditional attire. Matching jewelry to dress type requires attention to both the style and the occasion.</p><p>The foundation of jewelry coordination lies in balancing your look. Avoid overwhelming your outfit with too many statement pieces, and choose jewelry that enhances your overall style rather than competing with it.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bUfHBT": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Matching Jewelry to Dress Type",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Matching Jewelry to Dress Type</h2>",
            "custom_id": "match",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_qe4HYa": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Matching_Jewelry_to_Dress_Type_bded4cef-7ff7-4d84-94f9-32d01c1845f6.jpg"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_JmwFBb": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Casual Wear",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<ul><li><h3>Casual Wear</h3></li></ul><p>For everyday outfits, such as jeans and a blouse or a summer dress, opt for subtle pieces. Small <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/stud-earrings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Stud Earrings\">stud earrings</a>, delicate chains, and simple bracelets can add a touch of elegance without appearing overdone. These pieces are versatile and easy to wear, making them perfect for casual occasions.</p>",
            "custom_id": "casual",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Hm8Gfm": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Formal Wear",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<ul><li><h3>Formal Wear</h3></li></ul><p>Formal events demand a touch of sophistication. Statement necklaces, chandelier earrings, and layered <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/all-bracelets\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Bracelets\">bracelets</a> are ideal for evening gowns, cocktail dresses, or tailored suits. Focus on jewelry that complements the outfit’s colors and enhances its elegance. This is where understanding the best jewelry for formal wear becomes crucial.</p>",
            "custom_id": "formalwear",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_gHwqXq": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Traditional Attire",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<ul><li><h3>Traditional Attire</h3></li></ul><p>Traditional or ethnic outfits, like sarees, lehengas, or kurta sets, often call for intricate jewelry. Jhumkas, bangles, maang tikkas, and collar necklaces can elevate your traditional look. When choosing jewelry for different outfits, consider pieces that highlight the outfit’s craftsmanship and cultural elements.</p>",
            "custom_id": "traditional",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Jc4E4r": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Why Hallmarking Matters for 22 Carat Gold Jewellery",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Best Jewelry for Formal Wear</h2><p>Formal wear is all about elegance, sophistication, and making a polished impression. The right jewelry can elevate your outfit, highlight your features, and add a touch of glamour without overpowering your look. Here’s a detailed guide on selecting the best jewelry for formal wear:</p>",
            "custom_id": "bestformal",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_6WCWXy": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": " Necklaces",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h3> Necklaces</h3>",
