            "text": "<ul><li>Statement Necklaces: Bold, intricate <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/all-necklaces\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Necklaces\">necklaces</a> with gemstones, diamonds, or pearls instantly elevate evening gowns or cocktail dresses. These work best with strapless or V-neck dresses, as they highlight the neckline.<br/></li><li>Chokers: Elegant chokers made of diamonds, pearls, or delicate metals can add a sophisticated touch to formal attire, especially with off-shoulder or boat-neck dresses.</li></ul>",
