            "text": "<ul><li>Cuffs: Sleek metal cuffs or cuffs with gemstones can add a modern edge to formal wear without being too overwhelming.<br/></li><li>Delicate Bangles: Thin, elegant bangles create a subtle shimmer when paired with evening gowns or formal suits.</li></ul>",
