            "text": "<ul><li>Statement Rings: A bold cocktail ring with a large gemstone can act as a focal point, especially with minimalistic dresses.<br/></li><li>Stacked Rings: For a contemporary approach, stacking thin rings across multiple fingers can add elegance without drawing too much attention from the overall outfit.</li></ul>",
